he Golden Wayfarer was a mercantile sailing ship, originating from either east or northeast Faer√ªn, in the 14 century DR.The exact place of origin for the Golden Wayfarer is not specified but, as written in the Sea of Fallen Stars, it could possibly originate from either Aglarond, Altumbel, Impiltur, or Thesk.
This ship primarily dealt in the trading of spices.
The Golden Wayfarer operated in the Sea of Fallen Stars around 1370 DR.
